        <scopecontent>
          <p>The <title render="italic">Detroit News</title> Correspondent series (0.5 linear feet including 2 slide carousels and boxed slides; and an oversize folder) includes material related to terHorst's trips in his capacity as the <title render="italic">Detroit News</title> foreign and Washington correspondent. Of special interest are the visual materials included in this series: color slides with images from terHorst's European trip in advance of the 1959 Geneva Summit; color slides depicting John F. Kennedy's 1963 visit to Berlin; color slides and mostly black-and-white photographs from President Nixon's 1972 visit to China; and President Carter's 1978 trip to Africa. The series also includes <title render="italic">Detroit News</title> articles written by terHorst in 1959 and 1972.</p>
        </scopecontent>
