      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Documentaries</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Documentaries series (1 linear foot) is dedicated to two Elliot Sluhan Productions documentaries (<title render="italic">Air Force One: the Planes and the Presidents</title>, 1984 and <title render="italic">Air Force One: Flight II -- The Planes and the Presidents</title>, 1991). Material includes correspondence and personal notes exchanged between terHorst and Elliot Sluhan, and offices of the former Secretary of State Henry Kissinger, Presidents Nixon, Carter, Reagan, then Vice-President George Bush, and other dignitaries. Also found here are scripts, publicity material and photographs, and reviews of the documentaries. The series also includes both documentaries on VHS and U-matic tapes.</p>
        </scopecontent>
